						<summary>

						<p>A fragment lying out side the Anantēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">15th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary piece seems to have recorded a land grant probably to the deity of the place, the details of which are lost.</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 15th century A.D.</p>						

